&lt;p id="3jUMRR"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCOOP: Quentin Tarantino is recording a podcast&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="bq7ARO"&gt;The headline says it all. Quentin Tarantino, famed director of &lt;em&gt;Django Unchained&lt;/em&gt; and the &lt;em&gt;Kill Bill...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
